file_content.text: Our forward base in Capitol Square isn't much. Maybe you can aggressively negotiate us more space when you get there.
Can't believe you bought that sob story. We're supposed to be fighting the Empire, not rescuing scum.
We're going to show the Empire what we do to murderers. They'll be sorry they ever came here.
I wish you'd committed more to taking out those Imperial murderers. I hate the thought of that filth getting away.
This bleeding-heart Senator wants to waste our resources. Don't let him.
Colonel Brint, Eighty-third Battalion. Welcome to Corellia.
